  <li>Anda milik Parkland Avenue (harga yuran rata)</li>
  <li>Anda mahu penyenaraian multi-platform (5 platform)</li>
  <li>Anda menghargai pembersihan in-house (tiada markup)</li>
  <li>Anda mahu 60%+ hunian (rekod terbukti)</li>
</ul>

